lead_paragraph: Real Madrid know they cannot rest on their laurels after beating Barcelona and must beware a VfL Wolfsburg transformation in Wednesday's Champions League quarter-final, first leg, said coach Zinedine Zidane.

headline.print_headline: Real Must Be Wary of Wolfsburg, Says Zidane
headline.main: Real Must Be Wary of Wolfsburg, Says Zidane
